{
  "stem": "19210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was with the-- I served for a short period of time with the 2nd Battalion of the Jewish Brigade Group.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My commanding officer was Haim L-A-S-K-O-W, L-A-S-K-O-W, who later on became the Chief of Staff of the Israeli Army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- my drill sergeant was Sergeant Tal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, he also became a general of the Israel Defense Forces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we used to do some very, very, very basic-- basic training, like you do in any army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Ultimately, it paid off because we were able to use that training for the War of Independence, so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely, yeah, yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but when I joined the British Army, the-- the second time around, I left the Jewish-- the-- the-- the Settlement Police, and I went to-- near Tel Aviv there is a camp by the name of Sarafand.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very large camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came in all prepared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had promised myself, this time I'm going to be a liar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I came to the-- to the Joint office, I was asked for my papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, I'm sorry, I don't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you come to Palestine?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I came legally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where did you come from?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm a native of Bulgaria, Sofia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I came to Palestine via Portugal, because our family had ended up in Portugal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had lost all our papers, and that's how come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish officer in the room when I was being interviewed by the British.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the guy looked at me, he looked at me, and then when we went out into another hall, he said in Hebrew, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, you are-- you are Bulgarian like I'm a Chinese, but what do I care?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
